                      java.lang.String deviceID,
                      int severityID,
                      java.lang.String description)
Inserts a new event into the events table

Parameters:
eventTime - - time of the event in milliseconds passed as a long
deviceID - - Unique identifier of device
severityID - - Severity of event
description - - A description of the event to be presented to the user
Returns:
- true if 1 row was affected, false otherwise

insertIfNew

public boolean insertIfNew(long eventTime,
                           java.lang.String deviceID,
                           int severityID,
                           java.lang.String description)
Inserts a new event into the events table if and only if there is no existing event that matches the given description for the device.

Parameters:
eventTime - - time of the event in milliseconds passed as a long
deviceID - - Unique identifier of device
severityID - - Severity of event
description - - A description of the event to be presented to the user
Returns:
- true if 1 row was affected, false otherwise or if event already exists in the database
